<div class="project-description section">
  <p>After creating wireframes, we made a paper-prototype to test users to see how they used the app, and what we would need to change. The biggest challenge of this was setting the scene of being in the metro station, but luckily our app was pretty straight forward and the testers understood what to do.</p>
</div>

