<h3>Beyond the Device</h3>
<div class="project-image section">
    <img src="img/muse.jpg">
</div>
<div class="project-description section">
  <p>We decided we wanted to create an app that users could interact with not just on a phone, but in actual space too. This led to the idea of Digital Canvases. These would be set up in metro stations all over the city and display the top rated images from the gallery. Users would be able to interact with these boards by clicking images to view larger and  to see who posted them. These boards would also function as Wifi hotspots.</p>
</div>

